    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ (S.) Die sabati qui erat nonus exxeunte mense aprilis. Presencia <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum ominum</rs> corum nomina hic
                        subter leguntur, hi sunt <persName>Girardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs>
                        <persName>Lanfranci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> de <placeName>Casale Alto</placeName> et <rs
                            key="#parentOf">pater</rs> eius Lanfrancus iudes et
                            <persName>Martinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldio</rs> de Casale Alto. Ibique in
                        eorum presencia <persName>Ardicionus</persName> filius
                            <persName>Alberti</persName> de <placeName>Forminiano</placeName> et
                            <persName>Albertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> eius et <persName>Tedaldus</persName> de
                            <placeName>Adri</placeName> per lignum quod in suhis manibus tenebant
                        fecerunt finem et transhaccionem <rs key="#Churches">heclesie</rs>
                        <orgName>Sancti Benedicti</orgName> per domnum <persName>Anselmum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monahcum</rs> et <rs key="#Missus">missum</rs> de <rs
                            key="#Decima">decimis</rs> de <rs>bragidis</rs> que fuerunt quondam
                            <persName>Uberti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>. Penam insuper se obbligaverunt wiginti <rs
                            key="#Penalty">librarum denariorum bonorum Mediolanensium</rs> componere
                        siibsi per se aut per suos missos de decimis de bragidis adversus heclesiam
                        vel adversus successores eius agere aut causare presumsisent. Actum est hoc
                        loco Casale Alto, in <rs key="#Domus">domo</rs> Ardicionis feliciter. Anno
                        ab i[nca]rnacione domini nostri Hiesu Christi millesimo centesimo quinto,
                        mense aprilis, indicione terciadecima. Et ego <persName>Teuzo</persName>
                        iudex et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> rogatur hunc brevem scribere <rs
                            key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
